data.description:
Quaint 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home located at 403 S Litchfield St in Frankfort. This property offers a comfortable living space with a cozy atmosphere. The interior features a practical layout with a living room, kitchen equipped with appliances, and a dedicated dining area. The bedrooms are well-sized, providing ample space.

Nestled in a convenient neighborhood, this home is in proximity to schools and local amenities. Municipal Power helps to save money on the utility bill! If you're looking for a simple and comfortable living space, consider exploring 403 S Litchfield St in Frankfort.
